track_notes:
The track starts at the Balterswil Post bus stop. I took it on my way down and enjoyed it.
Just for completeness: My ascent started at the Itaslen bus stop which is closer to the summit, but the ascent is steep and partly without trail. Not recommended.
Longer hike from the centre of Wiezikon. Can be combined there with summit Burstel, HB/TG-009.
track_title: Ascent from the village of Wiezikon
